#. ~ Description for {'str': 'drone: e-cannon'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive drone: e-cannon'}
#: .\monsters\sq_drones.json
msgid ""
"An automated drone dedicated to electronic warfare. A large robot with an "
"EMP cannon."
msgstr "전자전용 자동화 드론. EMP 캐논이 달린 커다란 로봇입니다."

